data.description: This spacious home, situated on an expansive corner lot, boasts incredible potential for the savvy buyer. While it will need some renovations, the property features an abundance of bedrooms, offering versatility for customization and creative design. Envision your dream as you step into a large living room, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. The large lot provides room for outdoor activities. Embrace the chance to transform this house into your ultimate haven for entertainment and relaxation. Brand new HVAC and all new ductwork was added in 2021.
